 --------------------------------------------------------
Operating profits (Pounds m)              1990     1991
General Trade                               49       52
Motor and equipment distribution            78       58
Manufacturing                               39       29
Mineral extraction and refining            123      106
Leisure                                     30       16
Financial services                          16       25
Agriculture                                 25       24
 --------------------------------------------------------
Total                                      360      319
 --------------------------------------------------------
</TEXT>
