FT  27 FEB 92 / Observer: Bob's good job
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
If Manchester wins the Olympic Games in the year 2000, Bob Scott, the
theatrical impresario, will deserve more than the standard knighthood. He
has done more than any textile magnate to put the City on the map again, and
