Alastair Morton, chief executive of Eurotunnel and Elizabeth Symons,
high-flying general secretary of the FDA, the top civil servants' union.
Still, political demarcation lines have yet to erode sufficiently to allow
talk of a merger between the two tanks to creep onto the agenda.
